description:
The holidays may be over but here at Unqualified, we like to carry the spirit of giving well into the new year…which is why we’ve prepared this edition of ‘The Lost Tapes’ just for you – a collection of never-before-heard clips from some of our favorite 2018 episodes!

Enjoy!

  • BILL HADER talks about his project, Documentary Now, and re-making Grey Gardens (00:53)
  • SOPHIA BUSH brings in Something Weird, talks literature, and makes a plan with Anna to re-vamp traffic signals (9:58)
  • MACAULAY CULKIN bumbles into some dating app improv with Anna (27:43)
  • BILLY EICHNER talks to YouTube sensation, ‘Kali Fantastic’ (36:10)
  • ADAM RIPPON plays Would You Swipe Right and ponders what animal he would be (40:49)
  • ADAM SCOTT hilariously becomes Tom Cruise and drops some serious wisdom on Anna (60:25)
  • HEATHER GRAHAM does a red-carpet interview with ‘Beige Schumacher’ (71:26)
  • BILL HADER engages in a bit of Emmy Award improv (77:07)

 

Follow us!

Anna Faris: @annakfaris

Unqualified: @unqualified
